{"code":200,"message":"","data":{"id":"3906","movieId":"3903","title":"Daft Punk Unchained","tag":"社会·纪录片","desc":"Daft Punk，他们用开放的音乐态度，打破浩室、迪斯科和放克音乐的传统分野，开发变化多端的旋律、声响与歌唱，创造出幽默而不失深度，极富想象力的作品。","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/daft-punk.jpg","introduces":[{"type":1000,"text":"Daft Punk，他们用开放的音乐态度，打破浩室、迪斯科和放克音乐的传统分野，开发变化多端的旋律、声响与歌唱，创造出幽默而不失深度，极富想象力的作品。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/daft-punk01.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"以一首「Get Lucky」红遍全球的法国电音天团「傻瓜庞克」，成军20年来却极少公开露面，尔后更彻底以机器人形象现身活动。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/daft-punk02.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"法国导演赫威马丁戴皮耶的纪录片《傻瓜庞克：谁是傻瓜》，邀请到肯伊威斯特、「菲董」菲瑞威廉斯等大牌巨星，","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"横跨法英美三国的音乐製作人、乐评及音乐录影带导演现身说法，探索傻瓜庞克的创作历程，如何将向来由英美领导的流行音乐带向新纪元。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/daft-punk03.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"傻朋克著名于他们的表演皆经过精心的策划，并将视觉的效果及元素融入进音乐中、作品亦皆有如故事般的铺陈。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"自2001年以来，傻瓜朋克大多以机器人的扮相出现在公众视野，而他们的头盔以及手套就是其机器人扮相中很重要的标志。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"两人为了保持乐团的神秘感，基本都不会接受采访或是在电视节目里出现。","image":""}],"videos":[{"id":"3914","title":"【纪录片】被解放的蠢朋克 【2015】【法国】","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/daft-punk.jpg","playCount":"3","playNumber":1,"playNumberDesc":"电影","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d5623215\u0026cid\u003d9133202\u0026page\u003d1"},{"id":"3915","title":"Random Access Memories","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/daft-punk.jpg","playCount":"3","playNumber":2,"playNumberDesc":"音乐","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d2285300\u0026cid\u003d3562854\u0026page\u003d1"},{"id":"3916","title":"【Daft Punk】Alive2007，法国的电音天堂","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/daft-punk.jpg","playCount":"3","playNumber":3,"playNumberDesc":"电影","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d2795311\u0026cid\u003d4366499\u0026page\u003d1"}]}}